text: Yuliya Igorevna Anashkina (; born November 18, 1980 in Chusovoy, Perm Krai, Russian SFSR) is a Russian luger who has competed since 2000. She finished 16th in the women's singles event at the 2006 Winter Olympics in Turin. Anashkina′s best finish at the FIL World Luge Championships was 19th in the women's singles event twice (2004, 2007). ==References== * * Julia ANASHKINA profile at The-Sports.org ==External links== * Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Russian female lugers Category:Olympic lugers of Russia Category:Lugers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:People from Chusovoy
